reviewText: I'm in the process of rebuilding my music library after having it stolen and this group was at the top of my list for must-haves.  Only one more cd to go! I first saw The Elders at at Half-Way to St. Pat's festival at the Riverfront in Cuyahoga Falls, Ohio.  They rarely appear in Ohio, so if I get another chance to join them in the hoolie i will! Great energy and great music!
